  <h3>Primary Survey (ABCDE) + Stabilisasi</h3>
  <div class="flow-steps">
    <div class="flow-step"><div class="flow-num">A</div><span><strong>Airway + C-spine:</strong> Jaga patensi jalan nafas. Segera pasang cervical collar! (Dari kuliah pakar: sandal jepit + tali jika tidak ada collar — improvisasi!)</span></div>
    <div class="flow-step"><div class="flow-num">B</div><span><strong>Breathing:</strong> Pantau RR, saturasi O2. Jika SCI servikal tinggi → intubasi profilaksis. NGT jika distensi abdomen menekan diafragma!</span></div>
    <div class="flow-step"><div class="flow-num">C</div><span><strong>Circulation:</strong> Bedakan syok neurogenik vs hipovolemik. Pasang IV line, monitor BP &amp; HR.</span></div>
    <div class="flow-step"><div class="flow-num">D</div><span><strong>Disability:</strong> GCS, pemeriksaan neurologis lengkap, tentukan level lesi, ASIA grading.</span></div>
    <div class="flow-step"><div class="flow-num">E</div><span><strong>Exposure:</strong> Periksa seluruh tubuh (log-roll dengan inline stabilization!). Cari cedera tersembunyi.</span></div>
  </div>

  <h3>Farmakoterapi: Methylprednisolone (MPSS)</h3>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="pearl">
      <span class="pearl-label">AO Spine 2017 — Sering Keluar di Soal!</span>
      MPSS "dapat ditawarkan" (bukan wajib!) jika pasien datang &lt;8 jam setelah cedera, diberikan sebagai infus 24 jam.
    </div>
    <div class="table-wrap" style="margin-top:12px">
